skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: achiever beaver
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Achiever Beaver tracks the achievements you want, any achievement counts, eat an apple that's an achievement, walk for extra 2 minutes, that's an achievements.

No judgements, only achievements. 
No ToDos, only Dones

You can ask Achiever Beaver to list your achievements at any time from any day, this should brighten up your mood, and give you a morale boost.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
